Registered Vendor List

   The Vendors listed have registered with the USFA to obtain NFIRS 5.0
   development materials and the vendor validation tool. Vendors which are
   developing Incident Reporting software should develop their software
   according to the NFIRS Specifications and use the Validation Tool to
   test their output files. Vendors are requested to notify the USFA when
   their product development is completed and tested to be compatible with
   the national NFIRS 5.0 database standard. Vendors who have notified the
   USFA will be marked as "active" vendors on the Active list.

